{"tid":285440,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆話叫自己以後唔好返屋企","createTime":"2017-06-15T20:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T01:55:29.000Z","uid":88696,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8590697e75799075adc65b2cf0e98d1cb266b81b","tid":285440,"uid":88696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:34:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，老豆前兩日因為我借咗佢尿袋唔記得還，就半夜打比我大大聲好兇狠咁話搵唔到個充電寶以後唔好返屋企，唔好見佢，講完呢句就cut咗線，我到宜家仲覺得好hurt<br />\n<br />\n我已經幾日無搵老豆，就黎父親節，求問應唔應該破冰+點破冰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上係細細個我老豆都已經少係我身邊，物質同心靈上一直零支援。所以好多野就算未必認同接受我我都忍，我會不自覺咁怕佢會完全離開我，好似好犯賤咁<br />\n<br />\n我有啲嫌棄自己，但係又無辦法唔面對軟弱、想依賴既內在，好厭惡自己咁樣<br />\n<br />\n（有時候覺得呢種情況都會投射係宜家既感情關係裡面）"},{"pid":"61c23e46b17ac0b5d84b5d1ccd5ee7edc2172331","tid":285440,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:35:46.000Z","msg":"返我屋企吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f23f988cea16c6b9aed3ae5acda81d3009c0fb7","tid":285440,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e5c61b2bb58fae4dd617a5c0d0270fd3db6ea2","tid":285440,"uid":4210,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:36:40.000Z","msg":"充電寶你老母"},{"pid":"d67cbb6d131ebcbdadcf2a5a41b654301387a9f9","tid":285440,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:38:42.000Z","msg":"大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690135137f1aca666013a6ce6936535ee852a145","tid":285440,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:40:07.000Z","msg":"又尿袋又充電寶，新腥港撚？"},{"pid":"bfd455e2132d3f530f2809aa874044f08ebed1d8","tid":285440,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T21:15:42.000Z","msg":"唔好翻"},{"pid":"54bc952c2a752d04d3472e8fdf8287e1c37e8bbd","tid":285440,"uid":90978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T21:27:11.000Z","msg":"充乜撚電寳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1e8556f68cb79db62b9ca268031b122dae0eb0","tid":285440,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T21:27:54.000Z","msg":"父親節送個新尿袋俾佢同佢道歉囉<br />\n俾著我就順便串番佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ede50390b15e69439770d19ad2045384bcc549","tid":285440,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T00:16:35.000Z","msg":"咁你還番個尿袋 道歉咪得"},{"pid":"799deac0bf2fc2e5303d643b5fd439471d10cd44","tid":285440,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T00:29:05.000Z","msg":"咁撚小氣咪理佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170e506f9e520d020040cf4a1df42a7dd3776d5b","tid":285440,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T01:47:28.000Z","msg":"掉去將軍澳都唔比返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca77e0b9c7918d333efa7898ba69f7048a92838","tid":285440,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca3a9d0b79b3a4898acbaf9ac87c70bb3a1c73d6","tid":285440,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}